# (1) Requirements:

python -m pip install jupyter --user
python -m pip install pandas --user 
python -m pip install ase --user
python -m pip install seaborn --user

# (2) Then you will have to copy the source files to your working directory
(The working directory must contain the output files from the VASP run):

cp rapiDOS.py rapiDOS_analysis.ipynb ../calculation_dir
cd ../calculation_dir

# (3) Execute the code:
python rapiDOS.py

# (4) The code will create the dataframes and will automatically open 
the jupyter notebook in your default browser.
